* SMS Finisher Notifications. Automated SMS Alerts for Finishers
* When to use:      Run this live during the race to send instant notifications as participants cross the finish line.
* How to use:       Ensure the PHONE field in your database contains valid mobile numbers. Double-click the script to start the listener;
*                   an SMS is triggered each time a new finish time is recorded.
* Setup:            You must configure your SMS Gateway provider, API key, and "From" number within the Entries.INI file before use.
Announce            Headers
Announce Event      Finish
Sms Destination     Phone

* Message Construction
* Note: Keep messages under 160 characters to avoid multi-part SMS charges.
Message             Congrats 
Field               First Name
Squeeze
Space               0
Message             , you've finished the %race name%. 
Message             Official Results: https://results.raceroster.com/v3/events/%resultsid5k%/

/* Recommendation: Avoid including the finish time directly in the SMS. 
Times can change due to manual corrections or chip-to-gun adjustments. 
Providing a results URL is the most accurate way to share data.
*/

* Optional Time Formatting (Commented Out)
* Field             RACE
* Message           event, in a time of
* Event             Finish
* Minus             ChipStart
* Time Format       H:MM:SS.01